victory in last springs caucuses embarrassed the state into 
accepting a primary washington usually seen as a moderate 
politically progressive state carried the nations largest 
robertson delegation to the national gop convention in new orleans 
last august 
the measure already had cleared the house by an even greater 
margin since gov booth gardners signature was not required 
initiative 99 was delivered directly to the secretary of state 
minutes after passage 
champagne corks popped at an impromptu celebration staged by 
